	<h1>Research</h1>
	    
	<h2>Interests</h2>

	<p>
		
	I am genuinely interested in any topic that has to do with systems,
	software and security, and combinations thereof. Particularily, I enjoy
	working (and playing) with systems level software, tinkering systems to
	squeeze any bits of performance left and exploring large collections of
	historical software data to discover interesting facts or trends. As a
	consequence, I have also grown an interest in applying statistical
	techniques for analysing large volumes of data. My work so far has
	focused on the following areas: 

	</p>
	
